high_descs: Turn to the left and move to the silver table in the corner, then turn left and move to the middle of the television stand next to the coffee table, and turn right and face the television.
Pick up the candle next to the set of keys on the television stand.
Turn right and move toward the left arm of the brown couch, then turn left to face the couch.
Place the candle in the cardboard box to the rear of the credit card and to the left of the keys on the couch.
Pick up the cardboard box containing the candle from the couch.
Turn left, move past the television stand, then turn left by the fireplace, move to the middle of the coffee table, then turn left to face the coffee table.
Place the cardboard box containing the candle on the front left corner of the coffee table, to the left of the potted plant.
anns.task_desc: Place a cardboard box containing a candle on the coffee table.

high_descs: turn around and walk forwards a bit, then turn right and walk down to the end of the room, take a left and walk forwards a bit and move around to face the front of the small oval table
grab the candle off of the small oval table
turn around and move over to the front of the couch in front of you on your left
place the candle down inside the box on the couch
pick up the box with the candle inside of it
move around to the opposite side of the coffee table behind you, then face the coffee table
place the box down on top of the coffee table
anns.task_desc: place a box with a candle inside down on top of the coffee table

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk forward toward the table with the lamp on it and then turn left and walk in front of the TV.
Pick up the candle in front of the keys from the table.
Turn to your right and walk to the box on the couch.
Place the candle in the left side of the box.
Pick up the box from the couch.
Turn around and walk to the other side of the table in front of you.
Place the box down on the table to the left of the plant.
anns.task_desc: Place a box with a candle in it to the left of the plant on the table.
